Description: chromeless desktop-widget music player
 LoFiBox is a pure C++ Linux music player with a compact chromeless
 desktop-widget surface. It is designed around local playback, media-library
 browsing, metadata and artwork, remote-source extensibility, and a DSP-ready
 audio pipeline.
